ActPatent Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Patented Medicines (Notice of Compliance) Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the PATENTED MEDICINES (NOTICE OF COMPLIANCE) REGULATIONS will ensure that drugs authorized for sale under the Extraordinary Use New Drugs (EUND) pathway enjoy the same patent protection as other innovative drugs in Canada.
